bullets to disperse a crowd at an illegal oppositional rally in
Kabwe, 150 km north of the capital, Lusaka. Kaunda was to address
the rally.
</P>
<P>
Several other Opposition alliance leaders, including Liberal
Progressive Front leader Rodger Chongwe, and their supporters
were also injured.
</P>
<P>
