have good relations of friendship and cooperation. The policy of
creating a strategic partnership between China and Russia oriented
towards the 21st century, formulated by the leadership of the two
countries, has profound significance not only for the development
of the two countries' good relations, but also for peace and
stability in the Asian and Pacific region and the world as a
whole, he noted.
</P>
<P>
Speaking about the economic construction in China, Liu said
that China, adhering to Deng Xiaoping's theory of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics, has made considerable
headway in the economic construction, but it remains a developing
country with a large population. The task of China in the next
century is to continue to develop economy, he said.
</P>
<P>
When meeting with Liu Huaqing, Urinson said that Russia and
China have achieved great successes in their cooperation thanks to
the common efforts.
</P>
<P>
He noted that the meeting between Russian President Boris
Yeltsin and Chinese Chairman Jiang Zemin held in Moscow in April
of the year and the meeting between Prime Minister Viktor
Chernomyrdin and Premier Li Peng in Beijing in June of this year
pointed the right orientation for the two countries' cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Sergeyev said when meeting with the Chinese leader that Russia
sees China as one of the most important strategic partners in Asia
and the Pacific region.
</P>
<P>
"Russia and China have common views on many international
problems, while both of them need a stabilized domestic situation
in order to boost their economy. That is the base on which we
could develop our relations," the defense minister said.
</P>
<P>
Sergeyev emphasized that the strategic partnership created
between Russia and china is not an expedient measure, but a long
relationship.
</P>
<P>
The two sides exchanged views on other problems of common
interest.
</P>
<P>
Today's meetings were attended by, from the Chinese side,
Lieutenant General Qian Shugen, deputy chief of the General Staff
of the People's Liberation Army; Cao Gangchuan, chairman of the
Commission of Science, Technology and Industry for National
Defense; and Chinese Ambassador in Russia Li Fenglin; and, from
the Russian side, First Deputy Defense Minister Andrei Kokoshin,
Deputy Minister of Foreign Trade and Economic Cooperation Vladimir
Pahomov and Russian Ambassador in China Igor Rogachev.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese government delegation headed by Liu Huaqing arrived
in Moscow on Sunday for an official visit at the invitation of
Russian Vice-Premier Yakov Urinson.
</P>
<P>
Earlier today, Liu Huaqing and his delegation in company with
Vladimir Pahomov visited the Moscow International Air Show, held
in the town of Zhukovskiy near Moscow.
</P>
<P>
Urinson and his wife are expected to hold an official banquet
tonight in honor of Liu Huaqing and his wife Cu Hongxia. 
</P>
</TEXT>
