<HEADLINE> Chinese Premier Back from Visit to Malaysia, Singapore </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 26 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Premier Li Peng returned
here this evening by special plane at the end of an official visit
to Malaysia and Singapore.
</P>
<P>
Li's entourage who also returned here this evening aboard the
same plane included his wife Zhu Lin, Deputy Secretary-General of
the State Council He Chunlin, Minister of the Machine-Building
Industry Bao Xuding, Director of the Foreign Affairs Office of the
