architectural language will also be enriched," he said, adding
that it also strengthens the academic aspect of Chinese
traditional houses as the areas of researches conducted by
participants have focused more on a higher academic level.
</P>
<P>
The conference will provide a forum for renowned experts and
academics from around the world to exchange views and experiences
in the design and conservation of traditional houses and ancient
buildings.
