<HEADLINE> Sino-Swedish Sci-Tech Symposium Held in Stockholm </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, August 25 (Xinhua) -- The Second Sino-Swedish
Symposium on Sci-Tech Cooperation was held here today.
</P>
<P>
Birgit Erngren, director of Swedish Industrial and
Technological Development, presided over the opening ceremony. She
gave a briefing the scientific and technological cooperation
process between Sweden and China, and praised China for its rapid
development in the science arena.
</P>
