<DOCNO> XIE19970826.0259 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-08-26 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Brazil to Create Defense Ministry by 1998 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, August 25 (Xinhua) -- The Brazilian government will
create a new Defense Ministry before the end of 1998, said Chief
of the Military House Alberto Cardoso in a press release.
</P>
<P>
Alberto Cardoso said the creation of the new military
organization is part of a worldwide trend, but Brazil does not
want to copy models from other countries. He said the minister's
post could be granted to a civilian.
</P>
<P>
Brazil dose not have a defense ministry, but it has separate
ministries for the air force, the navy and the army.
</P>
<P>
The chief of the military house of the presidency denied any
relation between this project and the recent rebellion by military
policemen.
</P>
<P>
On August 22, President Fernando Cardoso met the country's
military ministers to discuss issues relevant to the creation of
the new Defense Ministry. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970826.0260 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-08-26 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Government Assistance In Central China Helping Feed The Poor </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Zhengzhou, August 26 (Xinhua) -- The fledging social welfare
system in central China's Henan Province is working on a security
net for the poorest of its rural population.
</P>
<P>
The provincial government began in May to provide assistance to
farmers who are getting by on a yearly income of less than 500
yuan (about 62 US dollars).
</P>
<P>
Though the amount of assistance is small, it can at least keep
food on the table of poor people and help them avoid starvation,
which is a priority in the country's poverty-relief efforts.
</P>
<P>
The government assistance is usually in the form of grain,
augmented with a small sum of cash, and is paid for by the county,
township and village in which the poor people reside.
</P>
<P>
This form of social welfare is now reaching some 4.9 million
people in the province with a population of 90 million.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970826.0261 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-08-26 </DATE_TIME>
