<HEADLINE> China's Investment in Light and Industry Goes Uphill </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 26 (Xinhua) -- Latest statistics from the State
Statistics Bureau indicated that the country's combined investment
in the light and textile industry hit 29.3 billion yuan, up 4.6
percent over the same period in 1996.
</P>
